                  <em>
                    This review has been hidden because it contains spoilers. To view it,
                    <a href="#" onclick="Effect.toggle(&#39;reviewTextContainer1136632448&#39;); return false;">click here.</a>
                  </em>
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1136632448" class="readable"
                    style="display:none"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer4110277306538668743">Fast paced with the perfect amount of time taken to explain concepts and provide background. What initially reads like a hubristic immortalization eventually turns into a cautionary tale of a dramatic rise and fall. Really well written!</span>

          </span>
        </div>


