      <div id="aboutAuthor" class=" clearFloats bigBox"><div class="h2Container gradientHeaderContainer"><h2 class="brownBackground"><a href="/author/show/762.Roger_Lowenstein">About Roger Lowenstein</a></h2></div><div class="bigBoxBody"><div class="bigBoxContent containerWithHeaderContent">
          <div class='bookAuthorProfile'>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__topContainer'>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__photoContainer'>
<a href="/author/show/762.Roger_Lowenstein"><div class='bookAuthorProfile__photo' style='background-image: url(https://images.gr-assets.com/authors/1227584992p3/762.jpg);'></div>
</a></div>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__widgetContainer'>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__name'>
<a href="/author/show/762.Roger_Lowenstein">Roger Lowenstein
</a></div>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__followerCount'>
345
followers
</div>

</div>
</div>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__about'>

<span id="freeTextContainer7921662109240537957">Roger Lowenstein has reported for the Wall Street Journal for more than a decade and is a frequent contributor to The New York Times and The New Republic. He is the author of Buffet: the Making of an American Capitalist<br/><br/>-HarperCollins</span>

</div>
</div>

